Author: ZeroEdge.Bet
Title: [ANN][Pre-ICO] ZeroEdge.Bet - A new cryptocurrency for online gambling
Body: Hi, concept wise we are indeed a bit similar to edgeless since we both offer 0% house edge games, but edgeless (will) have a smaller number of games compared to us. By no means marginalizing their work and effort, it has now been almost a year since their ico and they managed to launch only one game, also made some mistakes in the process that damaged their relationship with investors which in turn negatively affected their token value and image. To single out the main difference from a business perspective,I would say we have a much larger and experienced team as well as more versatile and accomplished advisory board to deliver the project which is on a bigger scale than edgeless
